        <div class="marker" style="background: rgba(124, 92, 255, 0.1); border-color: rgba(124, 92, 255, 0.25);">🚀</div>
        <div class="body">
          <div class="num" style="color: var(--glow1);">Indie · evenings &amp; weekends</div>
          <div class="title">Shipping the i*.today suite</div>
          <div class="desc">Nine apps live, three more in the oven. Each one started as a tool I needed myself — a secret scanner, an SSL alarm, a self-destruct link. I keep shipping because I keep running into problems with no good answer.</div>
